<title>Lal Messiah</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thiemgau te'n a genlawk uh Lal Messiah
 Kaisar nilopi ah a hung tungtai;
 Lal thak deihum ahi chawian hitiu,
 Lal thak deihum ahi chawian hitiu.

[V2]
 Aw van mithieng leh Belamputen,
 Miching zingzin singkhuola min;
 Chung si-al leh mi thiengtho te'n,
 Lawp takin Lalthak mimbang pieng ei hilh.

[V3]
 2. Lal cheng cheng Lal guolin a hung pieng puoi,
 Bethlehem bawng In tawmah a pieng ie;
 A min 'Mak' Lalpa' chu chawian hitiu,
 A min 'Mak' Lalpa' chu chawian hitiu,

[V4]
 3. A ngelten thakna'n van zai a vawl ui,
 &quot;Lei mi zatam singah cham leng hen,&quot; ti'n;
 Krista chamna Lal chu chawian hitiu,
 Krista chamna Lal chu chawian hitiu.

[V5]
 4. Hukdamna dak Lal Jubili aw chu,
 Lei leh van gam chengah a thang suok tai;
 Lal Immanuel chu chawian hitiu,
 Lal Immanuel chu chawian hitiu,</lyrics>
</song>